The Telegraph - Calcutta : Nation

 PM?s tips

 New Delhi, Nov. 5: Prime Minister Manmohan Singh has asked Union secretaries to implement the suggestions he made while addressing them last week, reports our special correspondent. 

 He has asked them to submit an action taken report by November 22 to the cabinet secretary and his principal secretary. They were also asked to list key objectives of their ministries and identify ?major performance-related milestones? they would like to achieve in this fiscal and the next. 




